page.title: 12A day in my life(10 yr. old)
page.content: A DAY IN MY LIFE This morning I got up at about 7:30am and got dressed,cleaned my teeth and put my shoes on. About 8:00am I got my swimming costume ready and about 5 minutes later I had a breakfast of crunchy nut corn flakes and after that fried bread and bacon with some orange squash for my drink.In my lunch for school I have a penguin,an apple,sandwiches and some crisps.I go to school and we all went swimming.We go to Romsey swimming pool and this week we had our swimming gala.I went in for the 25metres freestyle and the 50metres freestyle and also the diving contest.I did not get anything in the diving but in the 25m and 50m I got two thirds.When we got back it was playtime,and after playtime
